<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8">{{> base-styles}}</head>
<body>
  <div class="sheet">
    {{> letterhead}}

    <div class="doc-head">
      <div class="doc-eyebrow">Private &amp; Confidential</div>
      <h1 class="doc-title">Offer of Employment</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
      <div>
        <span class="meta-k">Reference No.</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{refNo}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <span class="meta-k">Date of Issue</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{generatedDate}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="salutation">Dear {{fullName}},</p>
      <p>
        Following our recent discussions, it is our pleasure to extend an offer of
        employment at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>. We were genuinely impressed by
        your background and are confident you will make a meaningful contribution to
        our team.
      </p>
      <p>The key terms of your appointment are set out below:</p>

      <table class="kv">
        <tr><th>Position</th><td>{{jobTitle}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Department</th><td>{{department}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Reporting Date</th><td>{{joinDate}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Work Location</th><td>{{place}}, India</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Annual Cost to Company</th><td>{{monthlySalary}} per annum</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Employment Type</th><td>Full-time, Permanent</td></tr>
      </table>

      <h2 class="section">Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
      <p>
        Your compensation is inclusive of all statutory benefits and is subject to
        applicable taxes and deductions in accordance with prevailing law and company
        policy. You will be eligible for company benefits as detailed in the employee
        handbook provided during onboarding.
      </p>
      <p>
        This offer is contingent upon the successful completion of background
        verification, submission of the required onboarding documents, and your
        continued eligibility to work in India.
      </p>
      <p>
        Kindly confirm your acceptance by countersigning this letter and returning it
        within <strong>seven (7) business days</strong> from the date of issue. We are
        delighted at the prospect of welcoming you aboard.
      </p>

      <div class="sign-row">
        <div class="col">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:10px; color:var(--muted);">For and on behalf of {{companyName}},</p>
          <div class="sign__space"></div>
          <div class="sign__rule"></div>
          <div class="sign__name">{{signatoryName}}</div>
          <div class="sign__title">{{signatoryTitle}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:10px; color:var(--muted);">Accepted &amp; agreed,</p>
          <div class="sign__space"></div>
          <div class="sign__rule"></div>
          <div class="sign__name">{{fullName}}</div>
          <div class="sign__title">Date: ____________________</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
